replies.body:
Difficulty for this item, and itemizing for marksmen in general, is AD Casters. A completely separate class of champions that can benefit (and snowball) from items meant for marksman. Honestly, you guys should consider separating melee and ranged only items more than just runann's and the hydras. Thematically, it doesn't even make sense for Ranged marksmen to be wielding swords... xD League of Legends has evolved past the point of "swords represent physical strength" and "staves represent magical strength." 

Having a melee/ranged version of nearly every item in the game could be a HUGE step to push unique champion identities and development. You could specifically target classes that abuse an item because that item only applies to them. Just brainstorming. :3

I think this item is just underpowered because mana return and physical power is a hugely abusive stat combination for AD casters. I think buffing it for marksmen could make it one of those top tier items for the mana hungry ones. {{champion:42}} {{champion:81}} {{champion:21}} {{champion:110}}
